---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: insights.html
root: ""
title: Insights | Green Wing Energy Solutions
description: Practical thinking on commercial energy — what actually moves the needle, and how to prove it.
canonical: https://greenwingenergysolutions.com/insights
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
{% set hubFeatured = collections.insightsSorted | featuredInsight %}
{% set rest = collections.insightsSorted | otherInsights(hubFeatured.url) %}

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="page-eyebrow">Thinking on energy</p>
    <h1>Insights</h1>
    <p class="lead">Practical thinking on commercial energy — what actually moves the needle, and how to prove it.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container">
    {% if hubFeatured %}
    <a href="insights/{{ hubFeatured.fileSlugStem }}.html" class="insight-featured">
      <div>
        <time datetime="{{ hubFeatured.date | isoDate }}">{{ hubFeatured.date | readableDate }}</time>
        <h2>{{ hubFeatured.data.title }}</h2>
        <p>{{ hubFeatured.data.excerpt }}</p>
        <span class="link-arrow">Read article →</span>
      </div>
      <img src="{{ hubFeatured.data.image | assetPath(root) }}" alt="{{ hubFeatured.data.imageAlt or hubFeatured.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
    </a>

    <div class="grid-3">
      {% for post in rest %}
      <a href="insights/{{ post.fileSlugStem }}.html" class="insight-card has-thumb">
        <span class="insight-card-thumb"><img src="{{ post.data.image | assetPath(root) }}" alt="" loading="lazy"></span>
        <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <div class="prose-wide prose text-center">
      <h2>Insights are being prepared</h2>
      <p>New practical articles on commercial energy optimisation will appear here soon.</p>
      <p><a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-solid btn-arrow">Arrange an Energy Review</a></p>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="topic-row">
      <span class="tag">Operations</span>
      <span class="tag">Measurement</span>
      <span class="tag">Sustainability</span>
      <span class="tag">Roadmaps</span>
      <span class="tag">Refrigeration</span>
      <span class="tag">Multi-site estates</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% include "partials/cta-band.njk" %}
